<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Music Albums App</h2>
        <p>
            View a list of different songs from different Country Music Artists.
        </p>
        <p><a href="http://musicappfinal20180401084833.azurewebsites.net/MusicApps">View a list of Country Songs &raquo;</a></p>
